comments: Abolished 1.10.1897 and added to the parish of Dethick, Lea & Holloway.
Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the parish of Belper.

Abolished 24.3.1889 and divided between the parishes of Idridgehay 
    & Alton and Kirk Ireton. See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Allestree, 
    Derby, Darley Abbey and Mackworth. See also Table 2, notes (c), (d) and 
    (e).

Abolished 25.3.1886 and divided between the parishes of Weston 
    Underwood and Hulland Ward. See also Table 2, note (a).
